Package main.util.constants

Class ElevatorConfigConstants

java.lang.Object
main.util.constants.ElevatorConfigConstants
public class ElevatorConfigConstants
extends java.lang.Object
Elevator Timing Constants contain how long it takes for elevator to perform actions.
Author:
Tony Zeidan, Evan Lloyd, Shaopeng Liu, Leenesh Kumar, YouHeng Zhou, Dominic Motora
